Add a `Lot` object to the `tender.lots` array, and add an `Item` object to the `tender.items` array. If this notice is a call for competition, set the lot's `.status` to 'active'; otherwise, set it to 'planned'.

Get the `Organization` object for the European Union; if none exists yet, [add a party](../operations#add-a-party), and set its `.name` to 'European Union'. Then, add 'funder' to its `.roles`.

Then, add the lot's `.id` to its `.relatedLots`. (PROPOSAL #20)
